{"tid":1801930,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"校長何滿添月中離世　校長遺願最想去利物浦晏菲路球場看一場球賽","createTime":"2019-12-29T04:56:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T11:08:50.000Z","uid":54373,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c100f48c42c9f8a8a67fac2fad64955bc5b82e7d","tid":1801930,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T04:56:52.000Z","msg":"黃梓維是「佔中」時期善德罷課活動的搞手，他表示，當年得到校長全力支持，兩人關係亦師亦友，何滿添近年身體轉差，梓維屢次勸他退下來，但他總是推卻。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">何滿添離世， 家人向梓維轉達校長遺願：「校長臨走前，最想去利物浦晏菲路球場看一場球賽，不知你可否代他完這心願？」梓維當日聽罷，一度跪在地上痛哭。</span><br />\n<br />\n「我出院了，在家中休息，有機會再來探我吧，再見。」這是何滿添對梓維說的最後一句話。梓維慨歎自己卻來不及跟校長道別，只願他可以安息。"},{"pid":"64f630dc143ff7d0f6d1263bedc9982e595a376a","tid":1801930,"uid":284463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T04:59:01.000Z","msg":"黃色經濟圈的障礙<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1801188\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1801188</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"598cdc7af92d20ee2fc03bec688dfef87cefcc28","tid":1801930,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T05:03:11.000Z","msg":"利 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e537fd7f8b22c342228ba5e0bc91d6ac534369d5","tid":1801930,"uid":192409,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T05:04:57.000Z","msg":"最後都做到區議員 總算對得住校長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c185ba7da71a2d70eae5933865566cac1eace6d9","tid":1801930,"uid":212897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T05:05:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29f78fa5e61995bfb19ca4f3db002e325b12e532","tid":1801930,"uid":196552,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T05:10:03.000Z","msg":"利物浦連支持香港既利迷既遺願都要破壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass